                            (2005), 1–42.</bibl>
                        <bibl>S.  Gero, <title rend="italic">Barṣauma of Nisibis and Persian
                                Christianity in the fifth century</title> (<abbr>CSCO</abbr> 426; 1981).
                            (contains a full discussion of sources)</bibl>
                    </listBibl>
